Special Files-------------------

page.tsx
layout.tsx
not-found.tsx
template.tsx
loading.tsx
error.tsx
default.tsx

Error Handing-------------------------

-Error.tsx file handles error for a individual segment(component) & its child segments(components)
-for handling errors in layout.tsx, put error.tsx in parent folder of the folder which contains layout.tsx 

Parallel routes-----------------------

-These routes defined using feature known as slots
-to define slots, we use '@folder' naming convention
-each slot is passed as a prop to its corresponding 'layout.tsx 

Intercepted routes-------------------------

- (.) to match segments on same level
- (..) to match segments one level above
- (...) to match segments from the root app directory